{
  "text": "Generation of caspase 8 conditional knockout mice. Epidermal-specific knockouts were obtained by crossing mice carrying the floxed caspase 8 allele (Casp8 fl/fl ) 4 to K14-Cre mice [CITATION_1] . Histology, in situ hybridization and immunohistochemistry. Please refer to the Methods.",
